data.description: 81 Wheelhouse Way in The Landings at New Riverside is a former model home and features multiple features that are an upcharge in new builds. The Summerwood upgrades include oversized cabinets, a massive quartz kitchen island with upgraded gas stove and beautiful backsplash in the kitchen with large pantry. The sizable owners suite includes high ceilings and great natural light, plus a bath that includes upgraded cabinets and spacious shower. This home also boasts a formal office with glass inlayed doors, large laundry, premium lighting, windows, and security system throughout.
